[To] Jarda Ynarow

[NPC Internal] Can you tell me who supplies your spices?
[NPC Narrate] -The Ynnwn turns from stacking mugs, holding the piled collection precariously before setting it down and looking at you.-
[NPC Narrate] -His expression is one of vague confusion. One of his brows raises in silent query, wordlessly asking you to elaborate.-
